 you have the game and all the playing pieces you need to get going and there’s even room in there for other stuff too.</font></div><div style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">Ideal entertainment anytime anywhere – at home, on the train, on the plane, or anywhere you fancy – any time is Quikky time.</font></div>')
