<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">How long should I wait for delivery?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">If orders are not sent by a timed or tracked service, please leave 14 days for UK orders and 30 days for worldwide orders before contacting us. We are not able to track orders and cannot make claims with Royal Mail until after this period for untracked shipments.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">Can I collect my order instead of having the order delivered?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Yes; we allow collections from our warehouse in Gosport. Please contact us to arrange a time and day, as collections must be arranged beforehand.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">How are you able to offer your prices more competitively than your competition?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Due to our streamlined business model and high levels of automation, we are able to greatly reduce the operating costs of the business, allowing us to run our business more efficiently and pass the savings on to our customers.</p>
<p>Our accounts with suppliers, combined with our massive buying power has allowed us to substantially reduce our purchase pricing.</p>
<p>We import from countries around the world, and these savings get passed directly on to our customers.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">What are your hours of operation?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Our official operating hours are 9AM to 5PM GMT, Monday to Friday.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">Can I have a bit of information about yourselves?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Absolutely - please visit our <a href="http://stores.ebay.co.uk/Racquet-Depot-UK/about-us.html">about us</a> page for more information about our company. If you have any further questions, we are more than happy to answer them - we would like to be as transparent as possible.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">What are your main areas of business?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">The company started business as a racquet sports specialist. Some years on, our focus remains within tennis, squash, badminton, racquetball, table tennis, as well as injury supports.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">What is Racquet Depot UK''s Mission?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Racquet Depot UK has the objective of becoming the racquet sports equipment retailer of choice in Europe, based on product expertise, pricing, quality of goods and level of service by placing the customer in the centre through an experienced, knowledgeable and dedicated team that are on hand every day of the week.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">Are all products sold genuine?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Yes; all products we sell are genuine and authentic. This means that all products sold and dispatched to our customers go through the correct distribution channels and most importantly, manufactured at the authorised brand factories.</p>
<p>Should you have any doubts at all, you are at liberty to contact any brand directly to establish we are an authorised reseller and secondly, ensure the product(s) received are genuine.</p>

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">What are your response times with emails?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">Our aim is to handle all emails within 12 hours, regardless of when an email is sent. In some exceptional circumstances, responses may take up to 36 hours. If you have not received any correspondence after this time period, please check your spam folder.</p> 

<p>
<span class="contact-faqs">How can you ensure I receive the best level of service?</span>
<p style="margin-top:-20px">We started business as an online only company and as a result, draft all of our resources into serving our customers. From a sleek, clear and concise website, combined with as much product information as possible, to a speedy and hassle free checkout process, we will continue to listen to our customers and adapt accordingly.</p>                        
                                
